844
01:05:23,760 --> 01:05:25,440
The tapes are the key.

845
01:05:37,960 --> 01:05:40,360
I ain't seen your ride, cabrón.

846
01:05:40,440 --> 01:05:43,000
Mrs Gayet?

847
01:05:43,080 --> 01:05:45,640
