864
01:06:21,560 --> 01:06:23,240
Hey, wait, wait, wait, wait, wait.

865
01:06:23,320 --> 01:06:25,200
A hotel card key?

866
01:06:25,240 --> 01:06:26,600
He's trying to play it straight

867
01:06:26,680 --> 01:06:29,600
